\section*{Conclusion}

The Hamiltonian Crystal framework allows \textbf{explicit calculation of both known dimensionless constants and new lattice-derived parameters}. Each constant is a direct consequence of \textbf{ratios of fundamental lattice scales and couplings}, providing a predictive, falsifiable model for physics from the vacuum up.

